### 1. Root Route
GET http://localhost:5000/
Accept: application/json

### 2. Register User
# @name register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aryan Sharma",
  "email": "aryan.sharma@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 3. Login User
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aryan.sharma@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 4. Get Profile (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Update Profile / Deductions (Requires Authentication)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "monthlyIncome": 95000,
  "taxRegime": "new",
  "deductions": {
    "section80C": 50000,
    "section80D": 15000,
    "nps": 20000,
    "hraReceived": 15000,
    "rentPaid": 18000
  }
}

### 6. Create Monthly Budget Category Limit (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/budget/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "category": "Food",
  "limit": 8000,
  "month": 5,
  "year": 2026
}

### 7. Get All Budgets (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budget?month=5&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Get Budget Status vs Actual Spending (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budget/status/current?month=5&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Log standard Expense (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "amount": 2500,
  "category": "Food",
  "description": "Weekly grocery list items",
  "date": "2026-05-20",
  "isTaxSaving": false
}

### 10. Log Tax-Saving Expense (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "amount": 10000,
  "category": "Investment",
  "description": "ELSS Tax Saving Mutual Fund SIP",
  "date": "2026-05-20",
  "isTaxSaving": true,
  "taxSection": "80C"
}

### 11. Retrieve Expenses List with filters (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses?page=1&limit=5&category=Food
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Retrieve Monthly Expenses category Summary (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/summary/monthly?month=5&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 13. Calculate Old vs New Tax Regimes (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tax/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "grossIncome": 1140000,
  "deductions": {
    "section80C": 120000,
    "section80D": 20000
  }
}

### 14. Get Personal Tax-Saving Suggestions Engine (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tax/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 15. Save a Tax Snapshot Scenario (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tax/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "financialYear": "2025-26",
  "regime": "new",
  "grossIncome": 1140000,
  "deductions": {
    "section80C": 120000,
    "section80D": 20000
  }
}

