### 30. Get Latest Salary Slip Details (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/salary/details
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 31. Get Salary Slip Upload History (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/salary/history
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 32. Finalize Salary Components & Sync to User profile (Requires Authentication)
# Replace placeholder ID with a salary slip ID from the upload/details response
POST http://localhost:5000/api/salary/analyze
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "id": "PLACEHOLDER_SALARY_SLIP_ID",
  "syncToProfile": true,
  "parsedData": {
    "basicSalary": 40000,
    "hra": 16000,
    "lta": 5000,
    "providentFund": 4800,
    "professionalTax": 200,
    "incomeTaxDeducted": 3000,
    "otherAllowances": 15000,
    "grossSalary": 76000,
    "netSalary": 68000
  }
}

### 33. Delete Salary Slip Record and File (Requires Authentication)

DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/salary/delete/PLACEHOLDER_SALARY_SLIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 34. Upload Salary Slip PDF (Requires Authentication)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/salary/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_slip.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf
< ./test_slip.pdf
--WebAppBoundary--  

